      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"meaning and impact\" thing just feels like something people say to be nice, you know? But it's not true. I don't have anyone here. I'm just a name on a lease and a face in a crowd of strangers who won't even remember I was there by next week. Everything feels so heavy and pointless lately. It's like I'm just taking up space that doesn't even belong to me. It would be so much simpler if I just... wasn't a factor anymore. If everything just went silent.",
